title: [Gyldemar Forest, Rocky Trail]
description: Weathered rocks cover the trail as it ascends to the north.  Water fills the nooks and crannies in the rocks.  Birds swoop in to take advantage of the little drinking pools.
Weathered rocks cover the trail as it ascends into the darkness to the north.  Water fills the nooks and crannies in the rocks.  Birds swoop in to take advantage of the little drinking pools.
